description:
Folks, the reason this episode has a date instead of a season 
and episode number is I am finding it hard to get the correct info on that.
There are several differing titles on the net.
So, this way the date is accurate as to when the episode first aired. Thanks :-)

Police Rescue is called to Glebe after a daring inner city raid. Two men attempted to rob a young man at knife point but were interrupted. Police search for a missing boy and stop a drink driver.
